            . I am servant to Sarah Etheridge, who is a <rs id="t18170702-131-viclabel738" type="occupation">dyer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170702-131-victim1029 t18170702-131-viclabel738"></join>. On the 24th of June, I found twenty-four yards of serge had been cut off from a whole piece that morning; the prisoner worked for us; soon after twelve o'clock I received information and went after her, I found her about seven o'clock and took part of it from under her clothes.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170702-131-person1031">
