                     <interp inst="t18170702-131-person1031" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mrs. Etheridge. the women left work at eleven o'clock that day, I saw the prisoner in the loft where the property is kept at twelve o'clock; she appeared very bulky.</p>
